data.name: NO WOVEN SWABS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Non Woven fabric made of 70% viscose + 30% polyester

## STERILIZATION
- Non Sterile, Ethylene oxide and Steam Sterilization

## PRESENTATIONS
- Sterile and non-sterile
- With and Without X-Ray Thread

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Absorbent

## AVAILABLE SPECIFICATIONS
- Non Woven Fabrics’ Quality: 30g/35g/40g/45g/50g
- With or without x-ray detectable threads
- Size: 2”x2” / 3”x3” / 4”x4” / 4”x8”
- Plies: 4ply / 8ply / 12ply / 16ply / 24ply / 32ply
- Packaging Qty: 1pc, 2pcs, 3pcs, 5pcs, 10pcs per sterile pouch, if non sterile: 100pcs/bag
- Package:
  > Sterile Package: Wrapped in sterile paper+paper pouch, paper + film pouch as well as blister
  > Non sterile package: white paper bag wrap
  > Colors: white
